query:
INSERT INTO
            leaf_aggregation_witness_jobs_fri (
                l1_batch_number,
                circuit_id,
                closed_form_inputs_blob_url,
                number_of_basic_circuits,
                protocol_version,
                status,
                created_at,
                updated_at,
                protocol_version_patch
            )
            VALUES
            ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, 'waiting_for_proofs', NOW(), NOW(), $6)
            ON CONFLICT (chain_id, l1_batch_number, circuit_id) DO
            UPDATE
            SET
            updated_at = NOW()
